Stan model files for hurdlebb.

Models are added in Phase 4 (Step 4.1):
  hbb_base.stan          - Pooled HBB, no hierarchy, no weights
  hbb_weighted.stan      - Pooled HBB + survey weights + scores
  hbb_svc.stan           - SVC with optional policy moderators
  hbb_svc_weighted.stan  - SVC + weights + scores + optional policy
